com.habelitz.jsobjectizer.jsom.api.statement
Interface ForEachStatement

All Superinterfaces:
JSOM, Statement, StatementBlockElement
public interface ForEachStatement
extends Statement

This Statement type represents an for statement that matches the forEach syntax.

The JSOM abstraction of forEach statements looks like 

      for (localModifierList type identifier : expression) 
          statement

Author:
Dieter Habelitz
See Also:
ForStatement
